body: We have a more extensive namespacing plan, where all the operators will eventually be in more appropriate sub-namespaces. So conj, abs, etc. will be in math. This is similar to say numpy where not everything is in the root numpy. I know in numpy we have numpy.angle, but we have already diverged on name.
